title: Juror in Ghislaine Maxwell trial testifies he made 'inadvertent mistake' when filling out jury questionnaire - CNN
content:
1. Juror in Ghislaine Maxwell trial testifies he made 'inadvertent mistake' when filling out jury questionnaire  CNN
  2. Ghislaine Maxwell juror who falsely answered questionnaire to testify Tuesday  Fox News
  3. Ghislaine Maxwell Juror Says He ‘Didn’t Lie to Get on This Jury’  The New York Times
  4. Ghislaine Maxwell's hearing in a sex-trafficking case over juror revelation should result in a new trial.  NBC News
  5. Ghislaine Maxwell judge grills embattled juror under oath  New York Post

description: A juror who voted to convict Ghislaine Maxwell of sex trafficking testified under oath on Tuesday that he made an "inadvertent mistake" when he filled out his jury questionnaire form, an admission that could upend her conviction.
